  fvwm-crystal-2.20040723-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc.

*fvwm-crystal-2.20040903 (10 Sep 2004)

  10 Sep 2004; Lukasz Strzygowski <lucass@gentoo.org>
  fvwm-crystal-1.0.1.ebuild, fvwm-crystal-1.0.3_pre1.ebuild,
  fvwm-crystal-2.20040723-r1.ebuild, +fvwm-crystal-2.20040903.ebuild:
  Version bump. Thanks for information to Daniel Webert in #62871. Stabilized
  older versions on x86, except 2.20040723, because it's buggy.

  15 Aug 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org>
  fvwm-crystal-2.20040723-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword wrt bug #59871.

*fvwm-crystal-2.20040723-r1 (12 Aug 2004)

  12 Aug 2004; Lukasz Strzygowski <lucass@gentoo.org>
  +fvwm-crystal-2.20040723-r1.ebuild:
  Added dev-python/pyxml to dependencies. Thanks to Jonathan Geisler in #59871.

*fvwm-crystal-2.20040723 (09 Aug 2004)

  09 Aug 2004; Lukasz Strzygowski <lucass@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +files/fvwm-crystal, +fvwm-crystal-2.20040723.ebuild:
  Initial commit of ebuild for new branch of fvwm-crystal. Upstream
  changed versioning scheme. Dropped ~ppc and ~sparc keywords because
  of new dependency - x11-misc/fvwm-crystal-apps. I will report it to arch
  teams. Added xsession file - files/fvwm-crystal. Added myself as a maintainer.
  Added description to metadata.xml. Thanks for testing to Andrzej Olender
  <arsen@gentoo.pl>.

  03 Jul 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> fvwm-crystal-1.0.3_pre1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

  14 Apr 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> fvwm-crystal-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Inherit eutils.

  01 Apr 2004; Tavis Ormandy <taviso@gentoo.org>
  fvwm-crystal-1.0.3_pre1.ebuild:
  more descriptive $DESCRIPTION.

